  <description><![CDATA[<p>The <span>Residence Les Temples du Soleil is ideally situated in the picturesque ski resort of <a data-udi="umb://document/50690c0f70c74050930d18799cab6fa8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/50690c0f70c74050930d18799cab6fa8}" title="Val Thorens">Val Thorens</a>. Its prime location gives you easy access to the world-renowned <a data-udi="umb://document/72a5198213b1400d8c891f49fe57b578" href="/{localLink:umb://document/72a5198213b1400d8c891f49fe57b578}" title="Three Valleys Ski Area">Three Valleys</a> and you can enjoy the incredible Alpine scenery surrounding the residence.</span></p>
<h2><span>Great location</span></h2>
<p><span>The Les Temples du Soleil residence is an ideal destination for those who want to ski, party and relax. Located at the bottom of the slopes, keen skiers and boarders can easily get onto the mountain each day, and with over 600 kilometres of pistes in the <a data-udi="umb://document/72a5198213b1400d8c891f49fe57b578" href="/{localLink:umb://document/72a5198213b1400d8c891f49fe57b578}" title="Three Valleys Ski Area">Three Valleys</a> you will not be short of areas to explore.  </span>The residence is a short walk from the centre of <a data-udi="umb://document/50690c0f70c74050930d18799cab6fa8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/50690c0f70c74050930d18799cab6fa8}" title="Val Thorens">Val Thorens</a>, where you can find plenty of bars and restaurants - once you have returned from a day on the slopes, or a day of walking or relaxing, you can make your way to one of the lively après spots which often have live music. For a more relaxed evening, head to one of the restaurants in town for a bite to eat - there are <span>places to choose from, be sure to try traditional Savoyard fondue or raclette whilst you are away.</span></p>
<h2>Fully equipped apartments</h2>
<p>The apartments are simplistic but have everything you need for your ski holiday, with a fully equipped kitchenette and living room with an additional sofa bed and a double bedroom. This accommodation is a great choice for families and friends looking for comfortable ski apartment with ski in, ski out access to the <a data-udi="umb://document/72a5198213b1400d8c891f49fe57b578" href="/{localLink:umb://document/72a5198213b1400d8c891f49fe57b578}" title="Three Valleys Ski Area">Three Valleys Ski Area</a>.</p>
<h2><span>Relax and unwind</span></h2>
<p><span>Unwind and rejuvenate in the residences own relaxation area which features a sauna, hammam and two whirlpool baths, this is not included within the package but is worth it for a moment of pure relaxation.</span></p>
<p><span>There is a bar on site so you can enjoy a glass of wine, or two, after a day of exploring the resort.</span></p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
